translation: Aaaaaarrrgh, my bo...my bodd...errgh... (insane ranting){#Name="Soldier A"}
source: Aaaaaarrrgh, my bo...my bodd...errgh... (insane ranting){#Name="Soldier A"}

translation: My bo, bo, bo-oo-oodd-erraargh... (insane ranting){#Name="Soldier A"}
source: My bo, bo, bo-oo-oodd-erraargh... (insane ranting){#Name="Soldier A"}

translation: The C-Cathedral C-City is... (insane ranting){#Name="Soldier D"}
source: The C-Cathedral C-City is... (insane ranting){#Name="Soldier D"}

translation: Wow. These skulls really class up the joint.{#Name="Zero"}
source: Wow. These skulls really class up the joint.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: You're not scared, right, Zero?{LF}You're not scared of this?{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: You're not scared, right, Zero?{LF}You're not scared of this?{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Nope! I'm not scared! Not one little bit!{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Nope! I'm not scared! Not one little bit!{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: But, Zero! Do you really think{LF}I'm stronger now? Huh!?{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: But, Zero! Do you really think{LF}I'm stronger now? Huh!?{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: But...I'd definitely be in trouble without you.{#Name="Zero"}
source: But...I'd definitely be in trouble without you.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Huh? Wow! Hey, say that again! Pleeease!?{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Huh? Wow! Hey, say that again! Pleeease!?{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Quit dancing around! You'll hurt yourself.{#Name="Zero"}
source: Quit dancing around! You'll hurt yourself.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: If all the Intoners die, the song that's{LF}driving your curse should, too.{#Name="Zero"}
source: If all the Intoners die, the song that's{LF}driving your curse should, too.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Then this batshit world can try to repair itself.{#Name="Zero"}
source: Then this batshit world can try to repair itself.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Intoners offer only pestilence to this world.{#Name="One"}
source: Intoners offer only pestilence to this world.{#Name="One"}

translation: Someday, they will be the disease that brings ruin to all human life.{#Name="One"}
source: Someday, they will be the disease that brings ruin to all human life.{#Name="One"}

translation: That's why you're trying to kill us: to save the world.{#Name="One"}
source: That's why you're trying to kill us: to save the world.{#Name="One"}

translation: And once you succeed in killing your sisters...{#Name="One"}
source: And once you succeed in killing your sisters...{#Name="One"}

translation: You're going to finish the job...and kill yourself.{#Name="One"}
source: You're going to finish the job...and kill yourself.{#Name="One"}

translation: And you'll use that dragon to do it.{#Name="One"}
source: And you'll use that dragon to do it.{#Name="One"}

translation: Well, you seem to know what's going on, don't you?{#Name="Zero"}
source: Well, you seem to know what's going on, don't you?{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Fortunately, I suppose, I came to the same conclusion.{#Name="One"}
source: Fortunately, I suppose, I came to the same conclusion.{#Name="One"}

translation: This world has no place for us.{#Name="One"}
source: This world has no place for us.{#Name="One"}

translation: Great! Then you won't mind dying.{#Name="Zero"}
source: Great! Then you won't mind dying.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: I know about your flower. I know it's behind all of this.{#Name="One"}
source: I know about your flower. I know it's behind all of this.{#Name="One"}

translation: And I imagine it's not going to let you die{LF}until it succeeds in destroying the world.{#Name="One"}
source: And I imagine it's not going to let you die{LF}until it succeeds in destroying the world.{#Name="One"}

translation: but since you don't trust me to off myself,{#Name="Zero"}
source: but since you don't trust me to off myself,{#Name="Zero"}

translation: you're gonna try and kill me first.{#Name="Zero"}
source: you're gonna try and kill me first.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Funny. I was thinking the exact same thing, One.{#Name="Zero"}
source: Funny. I was thinking the exact same thing, One.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: We've both been rejected by the world.{LF}We both feel the same threat.{#Name="One"}
source: We've both been rejected by the world.{LF}We both feel the same threat.{#Name="One"}

translation: And yet, here we are, fated to{LF}kill each other in the end.{#Name="One"}
source: And yet, here we are, fated to{LF}kill each other in the end.{#Name="One"}

translation: Yeah, destiny's a real bitch sometimes.{#Name="Zero"}
source: Yeah, destiny's a real bitch sometimes.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Oh, Zero. Still trying to be the bad girl.{#Name="One"}
source: Oh, Zero. Still trying to be the bad girl.{#Name="One"}

translation: I never did like that side of you.{#Name="One"}
source: I never did like that side of you.{#Name="One"}

translation: I felt like you and I might understand each other.{#Name="One"}
source: I felt like you and I might understand each other.{#Name="One"}

translation: What would some offshoot creation know{LF}about understanding? Don't be an idiot.{#Name="Zero"}
source: What would some offshoot creation know{LF}about understanding? Don't be an idiot.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: You too, Zero! Don't let your hands get hot!{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: You too, Zero! Don't let your hands get hot!{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Your hands usually feel nice and cool, Zero.{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Your hands usually feel nice and cool, Zero.{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: But sometimes they get real hot, too.{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: But sometimes they get real hot, too.{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Usually that's when your heart is crying.{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Usually that's when your heart is crying.{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: It's when you're lost and in trouble and...crying.{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: It's when you're lost and in trouble and...crying.{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: And right now, your hands are really hot.{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: And right now, your hands are really hot.{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Stop with the bullshit and kill that thing already!{#Name="Zero"}
source: Stop with the bullshit and kill that thing already!{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Zero... I know you know this!{#Name="One"}
source: Zero... I know you know this!{#Name="One"}

translation: If you want to kill an Intoner,{#Name="One"}
source: If you want to kill an Intoner,{#Name="One"}

translation: you need the power of a dragon!{#Name="One"}
source: you need the power of a dragon!{#Name="One"}

translation: If you think you're the only one suffering here,{#Name="One"}
source: If you think you're the only one suffering here,{#Name="One"}

translation: you're out of your goddamn mind!{#Name="One"}
source: you're out of your goddamn mind!{#Name="One"}

translation: You gave life to each and every one of them...{#Name="One"}
source: You gave life to each and every one of them...{#Name="One"}

translation: Then you went and killed them all!{LF}What did you expect?{#Name="One"}
source: Then you went and killed them all!{LF}What did you expect?{#Name="One"}

translation: You thought you could do everything by yourself?{LF}Well, THIS IS WHAT YOU FUCKING GET!{#Name="One"}
source: You thought you could do everything by yourself?{LF}Well, THIS IS WHAT YOU FUCKING GET!{#Name="One"}

translation: Ugh... You're the one who should be erased, Zero!{#Name="One"}
source: Ugh... You're the one who should be erased, Zero!{#Name="One"}

translation: Shut up! Shut up, shut up, shut up, SHUT UP!{#Name="Zero"}
source: Shut up! Shut up, shut up, shut up, SHUT UP!{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Because he was your sword, Zero!{#Name="One"}
source: Because he was your sword, Zero!{#Name="One"}

translation: You're a cursed Intoner!{LF}You're going to destroy the world!{#Name="One"}
source: You're a cursed Intoner!{LF}You're going to destroy the world!{#Name="One"}

translation: Where will you find a dragon...powerful enough to kill you...?{#Name="One"}
source: Where will you find a dragon...powerful enough to kill you...?{#Name="One"}

translation: If you're not here...then who's gonna kill me?{#Name="Zero"}
source: If you're not here...then who's gonna kill me?{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Stupid One... Who does she think I am?{#Name="Zero"}
source: Stupid One... Who does she think I am?{#Name="Zero"}

translation: I'll find a dragon somehow...{LF}There's...still time...{#Name="Zero"}
source: I'll find a dragon somehow...{LF}There's...still time...{#Name="Zero"}

translation: The Intoner Zero completed her objective.{#Name="Accord"}
source: The Intoner Zero completed her objective.{#Name="Accord"}

translation: However, the dragon Mikhail has died,{#Name="Accord"}
source: However, the dragon Mikhail has died,{#Name="Accord"}

translation: and Zero's mental health is in a rather alarming state.{#Name="Accord"}
source: and Zero's mental health is in a rather alarming state.{#Name="Accord"}

translation: I'm afraid there's little chance of finding a solution in this timeline.{#Name="Accord"}
source: I'm afraid there's little chance of finding a solution in this timeline.{#Name="Accord"}

translation: As such, I recommend sealing off this branch.{#Name="Accord"}
source: As such, I recommend sealing off this branch.{#Name="Accord"}

translation: There's gotta be a magic core controlling them!{#Name="Zero"}
source: There's gotta be a magic core controlling them!{#Name="Zero"}

translation: I don't know what that means, Zero!{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: I don't know what that means, Zero!{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: It's probably hidden in their bodies.{LF}Try killing one of 'em!{#Name="Zero"}
source: It's probably hidden in their bodies.{LF}Try killing one of 'em!{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Huhhh? How come no core came out?{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Huhhh? How come no core came out?{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: No! Over there! That one's got it!{#Name="Zero"}
source: No! Over there! That one's got it!{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Hey, did you see which one the core went into?{#Name="Zero"}
source: Hey, did you see which one the core went into?{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Uh...maybe it's the right one? No, wait! Left?{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Uh...maybe it's the right one? No, wait! Left?{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Ah, fuck it! Just destroy 'em all!{#Name="Zero"}
source: Ah, fuck it! Just destroy 'em all!{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Watch to see which guy has the core!{#Name="Zero"}
source: Watch to see which guy has the core!{#Name="Zero"}

translation: If you get it wrong, we have to start over!{#Name="Zero"}
source: If you get it wrong, we have to start over!{#Name="Zero"}

translation: I'm gonna hit my head if I fly around in here!{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: I'm gonna hit my head if I fly around in here!{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Maybe that'll smarten you up a bit!{#Name="Zero"}
source: Maybe that'll smarten you up a bit!{#Name="Zero"}

translation: That's mean, Zero! Look, I'm not flying in here! I'm not!{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: That's mean, Zero! Look, I'm not flying in here! I'm not!{#Name="Mikhail"}
